Company Description                    




                        Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC engages in the assembly of sewing machines. The company also manufacture cabinets and stands for sewing machines. The product also trades televisions. Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC was incorporated in 1963 and is based in Ratmalana, Sri Lanka. Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC is a subsidiary of Singer (Sri Lanka) BV.                    


