Singer Industries PLC Company Profile

 
			

Get an in-depth profile of Singer Industries PLC, including a general overview of the company's business and key management, as well as employee data and location and contact information.









 


IndustryAppliance & Tool
SectorConsumer Cyclical
Employees86
Equity TypeORD


Singer Industries (Ceylon) PLC is a Sri Lanka-based company engaged in assembling of sewing machines and the manufacture of cabinets and stands for sewing machines. The Company's product range consists of the traditional product lines, which include straight stitch, zig-zag and portable sewing machines. The Company is the subsidiary of Singer (Sri Lanka) PLC.


Contact Information


Address
RatmalanaSri Lanka



Phone
+94-11-2634416



Fax
11-2637151



